  "description": "Welcome to Casa Alma, a charming 2-bedroom apartment nestled within the brand new and prestigious residential complex of South Bay Las Mesas Homes in Estepona. Enjoying serene surroundings and stunning mountain & Sea views, Casa Alma offers a peaceful retreat close to all amenities.\n\nWith its contemporary design and bright interiors, Casa Alma provides a comfortable and inviting space for relaxation. The open-plan layout seamlessly integrates the lounge with the modern kitchen, creating a perfect setting for gatherings.\n\nStep onto the bright and lovely terrace and admire the panoramic views of the Mediterranean Sea and the picturesque mountains. Its enchanting mountain vistas and the glimmer of the sea add a unique charm to the setting, perfect for unwinding outdoors.\n\nFeaturing 2 comfortable bedrooms, including a master bedroom with ensuite bathroom, Casa Alma ensures a restful stay for every guest. Additional amenities include a laundry room, wifi, air conditioning, and dedicated parking spot in the underground garage.\n\nThe complex offers Mediterranean gardens, swimming pools, a gym, and 24-hour security for added convenience. Nearby, you'll find the Las Mesas Sport Club and Estepona Harbour, with beaches and restaurants just moments away.\n\nExplore Estepona's rich cultural heritage, enjoy a round of golf, or simply relax and take in the scenery. Casa Alma welcomes families and couples, providing a peaceful retreat in beautiful Estepona.\n\nPlease note that Casa Alma welcomes families and couples only, with no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. If you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and your group so we can assist you accordingly.\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you to Casa Alma, where tranquility meets luxury amidst the stunning surroundings of Estepona.",
